’Ů@c2fca3623ec90f50f347c5881d4f4586afce136e2cd5a4545a2454865661686bÚVTitle: title: is-empty
Path: Examples
Content:
Check if a string is empty
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> '' | is-empty
true

```
Check if a list is empty
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [] | is-empty
true

```
Check if more than one column are empty
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[meal size]; [arepa small] [taco '']] | is-empty meal size
false

```
